These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, british, chinese, mexican, polish, russian, canadian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, ice-hockey, golf, swimming, rowing, cricket
 1. the malaysian is between the mexican and the canadian##2
 2. the british is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the polish is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the mexican##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the canadian##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the russian##1
10. the polish is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the russian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | mexican | malaysian | canadian | british    | chinese | polish   | russian    |
| Sport         | rowing  | basketball   | golf | lacrosse | ice-hockey   | cricket | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: potato, nectarine, tomato, raspberry, eggplant, peach, lemon
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, japanese, american, dutch, british, malaysian
1. the british is on the far left##1
2. the person eating tomato is between the person eating peach and the british##2
3. the indonesian is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the person eating nectarine is in the middle##1
6. the dutch is on the left of the colombian##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the american##1
9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | eggplant | tomato | peach | nectarine | lemon | potato      | raspberry  |
| Nationality   | british | american  | malaysian     | japanese     | dutch  | colombian | indonesian |

