.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, italian, egyptian, american, colombian, malaysian, russian
7 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, snake, dog, chinchilla, bird, frog
 1. the colombian is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the russian##1
 4. the egyptian is on the left of the malaysian##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the american is the owner of the dog##1
 7. the thai is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the frog and the american##2
 9. the thai is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the italian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | russian | colombian | thai | italian   | american | egyptian | malaysian |
| Pet           | chinchilla | bird     | goldfish     | snake | dog   | lizard   | frog    |

