.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, milk, coffee, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, indian, dutch, egyptian, brazilian, thai
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the indian##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the egyptian##1
 3. the brazilian is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the egyptian##1
 5. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the dutch is between the person drinking milk and the brazilian##2
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the argentine##1
10. the canadian is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | milk    | soy-milk  | coffee  | mirinda  | almond-milk      | cola       | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | egyptian | dutch | brazilian | thai | canadian | indian | argentine  |

