.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, gospel, indie, jazz, soul, r&b, salsa
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, trike, jet-ski, roller, scooter, car
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the roller is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the fan of salsa and the fan of blues##2
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
8. the person driving the bus is the fan of jazz##1
9. the fan of soul is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | soul | blues | indie | salsa      | gospel      | r&b |
| Transport     | bus | scooter | car       | quad-bike | trike | roller | jet-ski |

