.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, architect, social-worker, dancer, electrician, security-guard, librarian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, biathlon, weightlifting, skiing, baseball, volleyball
1. the social-worker is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the electrician##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skiing and the freelancer##2
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
8. the security-guard is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | electrician | freelancer | dancer | security-guard | architect | social-worker     | librarian |
| Sport   | biathlon   | weightlifting    | volleyball    | skiing      | ice-hockey  | tennis | baseball |

