.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, tea, mirinda, almond-milk, 7up, juice
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, skateboarding, tennis, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person drinking almond-milk##2
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | water | sprite    | mirinda | tea   | 7up | juice    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | tennis | basketball | swimming    | baseball | sailing    | skateboarding | snowboarding  |

