.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, soy-milk, milk, iced-tea, 7up, sprite
The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, videographer, designer, entrepreneur, security-guard, scientist, bartender
 1. the security-guard is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the mechanic is on the left of the designer##1
 3. the scientist is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking sprite##2
 7. the videographer is on the right of the scientist##1
 8. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##2
11. the security-guard is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | iced-tea   | coffee         | tea     | sprite              | 7up    | milk     |
| Job        | scientist | videographer | security-guard | entrepreneur | bartender | mechanic | designer |

