.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, drama, crime, animation, spy, comedy
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, ship, boat, van, car, subway
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the van##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
9. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime     | spy | animation | drama | comedy  | time-travel |
| Transport     | ship | boat | van   | jet-ski     | subway    | helicopter | car   |

