.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, almond-milk, juice, lemonade
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, camping, filmmaking, rock-climbing, collecting, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | sprite  | water       | lemonade         | almond-milk         | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate        | juice |
| Hobby      | traveling | camping | video-games | rock-climbing | drawing | collecting | filmmaking  |

