3. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | gardening | photography       | video-games    | baking | drawing | filmmaking     | board-games       |
| Sport   | water-polo    | handball | basketball | baseball        | surfing | soccer | cycling |

