The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: thriller, time-travel, superhero, scientific, martial-arts, fantasy, drama
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, trance, soul, indie, ambient, metal
 1. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of metal##1
