 4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of indie##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
10. the fan of soul is the person watching scientific movies##1

